Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.26,0:32:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我可能说得不够清楚 但我跟你说过，叫你闭嘴不谈{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Maybe I wasn't clear, but I thought I told you to keep your mouth shut.{\r}
