Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.23,0:33:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你要我帮你甩掉这帮人{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}You asked me to get these guys off your back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.77,0:33:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}结果却变成 “来分’勒夫乔伊先生’一杯羹”{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Next thing I know, you're saying, 'Have a piece of 'Mr.Lovejoy.''{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.69,0:33:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我简直不敢相信我的耳朵{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I couldn't believe my ears.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.44,0:33:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我跟他们说我考虑考虑{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I told them I'd think about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.24,0:33:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}在我们这里，那有什么意义？ 空话一句{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}In this town, what does that mean? Nothing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.03,0:33:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}这就是你跟我不一样的地方{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}That's the difference between you and me, Harry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.24,0:33:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我不说空话{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I say what I mean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.83,0:33:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}如果想跟某人要某样东西 我会跟他们直说{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}If I want something from someone, I ask them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.58,0:33:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}如果要马丁威尔 我会直接找马丁威尔{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}If I want Martin Weir, I go get Martin Weir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.04,0:33:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我不会跟他的健身教练的 心理医生瞎搅和{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I don't fuck around with his trainer's shrink.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.54,0:33:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}- 是心理医生的健身教练 - 送我到我车子那{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Shrink's trainer. Take me back to my car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.39,0:33:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}- 喂？你跑去哪里？ - 我是汤米，阿智{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}- Tommo? Chili. - Where you been?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.31,0:33:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}到处打电话都找不到你{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I been calling all over for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.31,0:33:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}雷朋斯在找你，你死哪去了？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Ray Bones is looking for you. Where the hell are you?{\r}
