Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.36,0:33:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我要进入电影圈 正在考虑要当制片{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Going into the movie business. I'm thinking about producing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.49,0:34:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}电影制作你懂个屁啊？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}What the fuck do you know about making movies?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.41,0:34:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}制片不需要懂太多{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I don't think the producer has to know much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.49,0:34:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你说的要不是屁话就是呆话{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I think you're full of shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.33,0:34:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我得挂断了{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I gotta go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.21,0:34:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}等你了解雷朋斯多一点后 再打电话给我{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Call me when you know more about Ray Bones.{\r}
