Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.96,0:34:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你又来干嘛？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}What are you doing here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.67,0:34:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我来向你道歉的 因为昨晚破门而入{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I wanted to apologize for breaking in last night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.88,0:34:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}这是什么道理{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Let me get this straight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.84,0:34:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你破门而入来 为前次破门而入道歉？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}You broke in again to apologize for breaking in before?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.18,0:34:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}不，你阳台门开着{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Your patio door was open.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.89,0:34:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你应该锁门 你家里好东西不少{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}You shouldn't do that. You got nice things in here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.35,0:34:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}出去时记得锁门{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Make sure you lock it on the way out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.52,0:34:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}今天过得不顺吗？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Bad day?{\r}
