Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.20,0:34:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}什么？显然他没看过 你的“变种人新娘”{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}What? Obviously he didn't see you in 'Bride of the Mutant.'{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.20,0:34:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你看过？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}You saw that?{\r}
