Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.37,0:34:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}跟异形妈妈说 她在地球的日子结束时{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}and say to the alien mother that her time on Earth is finished...{\r}
