Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.38,0:34:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}有你在那场戏里表达的 感情和张力{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}in her day, the intensity you had in that scene.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.63,0:35:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}那场戏还不错啦… 我的意思是以恐怖电影来说{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}That was a good scene. I mean, for a horror movie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.01,0:35:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}不，以任何标准来看都是{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}For any movie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.35,0:35:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我知道我不只如此{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I'm better than what I've been doing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.81,0:35:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}不是胸大无脑 只会时间一到就尖叫而已{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}wearing fuck-me pumps and a tank top, waiting 'til it was time to scream.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.56,0:35:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}- 但你叫得很好听 - 对，那是我天生的本钱{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}But what a scream. It's a real gift.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.86,0:35:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我的意思是，如果有机会说一句 伟大的台词也很棒{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}All I'm saying is it'd be nice to get the chance to say one great line.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.40,0:35:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}好比贝蒂戴维斯 在“棉田小屋”里{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Like in that great Bette Davis movie, 'Cabin in the Cotton'...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.36,0:35:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}她走向一个用眼光挑逗她的人{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}where she walks up to the guy, gives him a look...{\r}
