Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.20,0:35:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}好台词，你怎么 不拍哈利的电影了？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Great line. How come you don't do movies with Harry anymore?{\r}
