Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.17,0:35:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}他应该是说“异形怪物3”之后{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}He must mean after 'Slime Creatures III.'{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.72,0:35:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}所以哈利昨晚过来…{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Was that why Harry came over last night?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.84,0:35:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}请你帮他说服马丁拍一部电影？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}To ask you to help him put Martin in a movie?{\r}
