Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.27,0:35:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}他根本拍不成{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}he'll get off the ground...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.14,0:35:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}不管我帮不帮他 他都签不下一个大明星{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}with a star he'll never sign, with or without my help.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.10,0:35:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}- 他说马丁对剧本非常有兴趣 - 马丁对任何东西都很有兴趣{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}He said Martin flipped over it. Martin's known for his flipping.{\r}
