Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.36,0:36:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我到哈利办公室拿一份剧本给你{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Why don't I go to Harry's office and get a copy of the script?{\r}
