Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.99,0:41:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你对这个案子一定有重大贡献{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}You must bring something heavy to the deal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.95,0:41:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}的确- - 那就是我{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I do. Me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.78,0:41:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}听说你可以邀请马丁威尔 来饰演勒夫乔伊？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}It says here you're getting Martin Weir for the part of Lovejoy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.75,0:41:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}没错，我们要请马丁{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}That's right. Martin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.29,0:41:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我不信 你打算怎么请？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Come on. How you gonna do that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.00,0:41:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我会拿把枪指着他的脑袋{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I'm gonna put a gun to his head and say...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.71,0:41:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}说“签字，马丁，不然就没命” 就这样{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}'Sign the fucking papers, Martin, or you're dead.' That's it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.46,0:41:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我怀疑这招有效吗？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I wonder, would that work?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.34,0:41:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你知道我认为谁适合 演艾尔罗西吗？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}You know who I see for the part of Al Roxy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.09,0:42:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}哈维凯托 简直是为他量身订做的{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Harvey Keitel. Man could play it in his sleep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.30,0:42:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}他在“手指”里的演出很精彩{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}He was pretty good in the movie 'Fingers.'{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.97,0:42:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}没看过 你知道还有谁适合吗？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Missed it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.48,0:42:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}摩根费里曼 摩根的电影你熟吗？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}You know who else? Morgan Freeman. You know his work?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.31,0:42:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}摩根费里曼，但他是黑人{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Morgan Freeman, yeah. But he's a colored guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.48,0:42:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}那又怎么样？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}So what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.32,0:42:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}剧本里有说他是白人吗？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Where's it say in the script the man's got to be white?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.99,0:42:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}这个角色需要加点颜色 演这个角色的人要有特殊风格{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Color's what the part needs, man. Somebody to do it with some style.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.53,0:42:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你觉得剧本怎么样？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}What do you think of the script?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.58,0:42:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}（辛制片公司）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.29,0:42:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}首先，片名要改{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}First thing that's got to go is the title.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.92,0:42:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}用编剧的名字墨瑞沙佛林 都比勒夫乔伊好{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}The writer's name, Murray Saffrin, would be better than Lovejoy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.96,0:42:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}这点我同意{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I'm with you on that one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.84,0:42:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你知道我有什么主意吗？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}You know what I'm thinking?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.63,0:42:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我们两个好好坐下来 剧本写不好的地方，我们来改写{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Why don't you and I rewrite the script where it needs it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.97,0:42:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你会写剧本？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}You could write one?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.51,0:42:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}写剧本有什么了不起{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}There's nothing to it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.31,0:42:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}先想好点子 再把它写在纸上{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}All you do, you get an idea. Set down what you want to say on paper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.60,0:42:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}然后请一个枪手 在正确的地方补上逗点等等符号{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Then you hire someone else to fill in the commas and shit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.73,0:42:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}如果你自己不太确定的话{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}where they belong, if you're not positive yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.19,0:42:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}或许也订正一下某些艰深的字{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Maybe fix up the spelling where you have some tricky words.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.49,0:42:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我看过一些剧本，里面错字连篇{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Although I've seen some scripts I know the words weren't spelled right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.86,0:43:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}甚至连逗点都不用 所以我认为这不太重要{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}There were hardly any commas at all, so I don't think that's too important.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.87,0:43:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}好啦，要结束时 你就写“淡出”然后就完成了{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}You get to the end. You write in, 'Fade out.' You're done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.21,0:43:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}就这样 写剧本这么简单？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}That's it? That's all there is?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.88,0:43:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}那我要你干嘛？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Then what the fuck do I need you for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.84,0:43:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}因为我愿意为这部片效命{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Because I'm offering my services on this one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.88,0:43:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我来跟你说 需要你效劳的时候{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Tell you what. If I need a ride sometime...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.72,0:43:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我会告诉你{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I'll let you know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.60,0:43:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你怎么可以在这里逮捕我？ 这是我的国家{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}How could you arrest me here? This is my country.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.48,0:43:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}这是你送命的地方{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}This is where you're going to die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.61,0:43:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}这不是点火失败 是叫你转过身来{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}That was no misfire! That was to turn you around...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.07,0:43:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我不想对你的背后开枪{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}'cause I don't want to shoot you in the back...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.41,0:43:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}除非你还是选择逃跑{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}unless you'd rather try to run from me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.91,0:43:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}史瓦兹，她在那里吗？ 你有带我太太来吗？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Is she there? Did you bring my wife?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.00,0:43:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}她在车子里 全部都录下来了{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}She's in the car. They've got it all on tape.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.42,0:43:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}- 你确定录得够多？ - 播出来听你就知道了{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}- You sure you got enough? - Play it back. You'll see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.63,0:44:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你陷害了多少人？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}How many did you frame?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.43,0:44:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}- 那把枪最好给我 - 好，拿去{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}- You better give me that gun. - Okay, here it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.18,0:44:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}“这是我帮你挡下的 第二颗子弹”{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}That's the second bullet I've stopped for you. That's the second bullet I've stopped for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.19,0:44:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你死定了，奥森{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}You're going down, Orson.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.95,0:44:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}不是有人该进来把他带走吗？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Isn't somebody going to come and take him away?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.08,0:44:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}对，等一下 你真的喜欢他，对吧？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}In a few minutes. You really liked him, didn't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.29,0:44:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}“条子喜欢他”{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}The cop did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.60,0:44:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}杀他的那一个{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}The cop did. The one who killed him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.29,0:44:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}“他喜欢他”{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}- He loved him. - He loved him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.09,0:44:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}汉克算是个好侦探{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}He was a great detective.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.84,0:44:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}“但他是很差劲的条子”{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}- But a lousy cop. - And a lousy cop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.30,0:44:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你对他只有这句话？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Is that all you have to say for him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.22,0:44:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}他是个很有个性的人{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}He was some kind of a man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.31,0:44:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你对他人的评语有什么作用？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}What does it matter what you say about people?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.78,0:45:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}再见，谭雅 再会{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}- Good-bye, Tanya. - Adios.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.60,0:45:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}再会{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Adios.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.12,0:45:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}（剧终）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.62,0:45:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}哇，噢？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Whoo{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.01,0:45:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}你一直在这里？{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}You've been here the whole time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.43,0:45:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}没有，刚好赶上结局{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I just caught the end.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.80,0:45:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}知道吗 威尔斯根本不想拍这部片{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Welles didn't even want to do this movie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.18,0:45:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}但他被制片厂的合约绑住了{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}He had some studio contract he couldn't get out of.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.18,0:45:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}有时候你拍出最好的作品 因为别人用枪抵着你的脑袋{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Sometimes you do your best work when you got a gun to your head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.98,0:45:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}对{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Yeah{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.23,0:45:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我帮你带剧本来了{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}I brought the script.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.82,0:45:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}我看过了，哈利留了一本在我家{\r}\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\bord1\shad1\3c&H924F1B&}Harry left a copy at my house.{\r}
